version_description: So far, no english chords available, so I am writing one.
The chords are directly taken from the LIVE version ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-t6iezoBTDw ).

Acoustic version found under the youtube account of Worship tutorials. In the video the guy messed up the lyrics, he didn't play the final Chorus, but put that in this after listening to the song. Little bit different chords than on electric. Enjoy and please rate and leave comments.
Simplest version I have found working for me with an easy strumming pattern.
Acoustic version found under the youtube account of Worship tutorials. Key of G with so it is more suited for male vocalists, easy version of Bm to make chord changes easier.
